<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="lock-v">lock <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /lɒk/    美 /lɑːk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>锁上；锁住：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The door doesn't lock.
这门锁不上。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You were silly not to have locked your car. 
你没把车锁上真是太糊涂了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Oliver was immediately <strong>locked in</strong> a room.  
奥利弗立刻被锁进一间屋子里。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 3</footer></div></div>